   <conbody>
      <p class="- topic/p ">Each system has a plinth at the bottom of the cabinet with the
height of 100 mm. The plinth needs to be fastened to the floor at
the installation site.</p>
      <p class="- topic/p ">For dimensions and details of the plinth, see the <i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">Drawings</i>.</p>
      <note type="important" class="- topic/note ">Always fasten the cabinet to the floor before
connecting any cables.</note>
      <ul class="- topic/ul ">
         <li class="- topic/li ">
            <p class="- topic/p ">The locations <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">(A)</b> are accessed from the back of the
cabinet between the plinths with the back plinth plate cover removed.</p>
         </li>
         <li class="- topic/li ">
            <p class="- topic/p ">The locations <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">(B)</b> are accessed from the front of the
cabinet between the plinths with the front plinth plate cover removed.</p>
         </li>
      </ul>
